# Real_World_Examples: ignore regenerable run outputs / scratch / lock files only.
# NOTE: asp_files/, ilasp_tasks/, learned_encodings/, neg_generator/ are committed
# on purpose -- they are a hand-curated, not-yet-reproducible dataset (see audit),
# so they are treated as source until the Exp2 rebuild is made reproducible.
